Package xxl.core.relational.tuples

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ColumnComparableTuple
    A tuple is a hard copy (materialization) of an (existing) tuple of a result set.
    Tuple
    A tuple is a hard copy (materialization) of an (existing) tuple of a result set.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractTuple
    This class is a skeleton-implementation for a tuple.
    ArrayTuple
    Implements an array-tuple where the column objects are packed together in an object array.
    ColumnComparableArrayTuple  
    ComparableTuples
    The ComparableTuples class provides various algebraic or useful methods for dealing with tuple objects .
    ListTuple
    Implements a list-tuple where the column objects are saved in a list.
    ProjectedTuple
    Makes a projection of a tuple to certain columns.
    TupleConverter
    This class is a converter for tuples which converts a tuple into a byte value in order to read or write a tuple.
    Tuples
    This class contains various useful static methods for Tuples.
    WrappedTuple
    This class provides an extended decorator for tuples.
